International Collaboration Model
The role does not require interaction with the team in Poland. Daily collaboration takes place with Mack Fak in Milan, the KGYZ Finance Team in Boston, and Matrix Manager Jan Sobieski. All key stakeholders are geographically distributed, and cooperation is conducted fully virtually.

Subject Matter Expertise Role
Acts as Subject Matter Expert for key financial models, including KKK Model, GGG Model, and XXX Model. Responsibilities are analytical and outcome-based, with performance measured by quality and delivery rather than physical presence.

Operational Efficiency
The nature of the role and global stakeholder structure make full remote work operationally effective, without impact on communication, productivity, or business continuity.
